{"tid":703411,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個話世界杯咁大型咁隆重冇假波？","createTime":"2018-06-15T17:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T17:34:49.000Z","uid":22791,"like":10,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a398061c1d46a49f3036f9863e73cfb2fc7d0f66","tid":703411,"uid":22791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T17:13:36.000Z","msg":"睇咗頭3場 真係笑撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n揭幕戰 沙地輸緊踢到好似贏緊3粒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲後衛俾人逼搶都慢慢扭 唔講以為係沙地美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n烏龜嗰場就收咗order唔俾入波 蘇狗單刀炒足咁多球 有球單刀癲到空哂都唔撚射 繼續推前俾龍門沒收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n伊朗呢場仲撚癲 妹足90分鐘 開個罰球 摩哥條友可以喺空哂既情況下 怒頂入自己龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頂得靚撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係見佢著住套紅色衫仲以為佢係伊朗嗰邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個個以為4年1次既世界盃 個個球員攞命搏為國爭光 唔會打假<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實世界盃就係俾班莊嚟掠水<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b2fc20b55585ab356aed94262cbafb687cae8f","tid":703411,"uid":58140,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T17:14:11.000Z","msg":"2002年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e299e50479679be4c9851551ccab86f74b401e6","tid":703411,"uid":4308,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T17:15:14.000Z","msg":"輸好多？"},{"pid":"64a4acf4aafda3f1ba2bfe260d67e6a680a18f7a","tid":703411,"uid":14739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T17:15:16.000Z","msg":"點會冇假波呀<br />\n比莊家收錢用<br />\n4年1次cap 盡"},{"pid":"bd0946499820166dc8e8e5d97a39e84a0f2f6eb9","tid":703411,"uid":128057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T17:15:26.000Z","msg":"烏龍球個下真係